title: Theodore Roosevelt Island: Photos & Multimedia
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Photos & Multimedia             Photos & Multimedia                    Developing the Memorial   8 Photos  Explore proposed memorials to Theodore Roosevelt that were never approved, and see photos of the Civilian Conservation Corps at work developing the memorial design that was finally chosen.                               Minute Out in It: Spring Peepers   Loading the player...       Visit JWPlayer docs for keyboard shortcuts  Duration:32 seconds  A non-stop chorus of tiny frogs sings from small pools near the north end of the boardwalk on the Swamp Trail.               Minute Out in It: Mystery Digger   Loading the player...       Visit JWPlayer docs for keyboard shortcuts  Duration:23 seconds  A ranger was walking the Swamp Trail, looking for signs of spring, when the earth started to pulse. The cause of all this movement never did appear...
